                                            <p><m>x=0 \Rightarrow y=2\cdot(0)+(0)^2=0+0=0 \therefore </m>E=(0,0)</p>
                                            <p><m>x=1 \Rightarrow y=2\cdot(1)+(1)^2=2+1=3 \therefore </m>F=(1,3)</p>
